      • Vehicle

        public Vehicle(Coordinate position,
               double speed,
               Path path,
               java.util.List<java.lang.Integer> times,
               int goEveryXMinute,
               int startMinute)
        Vehicle constructor (calls setNumber() and setGui())
        Parameters:
        position - Starting position
        speed - Vehicle default speed
        path - Path (list of Coordinates) including crossroads
        times - List of timetable times is seconds (how long does it take to go to next stop)
        goEveryXMinute - How often does the vehicle go (in minutes, etc. 3 means every 3 minutes)
        startMinute - Start offset (in minutes, etc. 5 means the first bus goes :05 )
